data.description: *2.25% Interest Assumable VA Loan! Must be eligible for a VA Loan to qualify.* Charming 4 bedroom 2.5 bath better than new home in Dallas! Built in 2020 by Fischer Homes in the highly desirable neighborhood of Edenwood! Enjoy cooking in this stylish kitchen with spacious cabinetry, a large center island, and a walk-in pantry. Updated modern cabinet hardware throughout home, granite countertops throughout, nicely stained back deck and beautiful LVP on the entire main level! Easily flow from room to room with this great floor plan. The large primary bedroom features a gorgeous black accent wall, with sliding barn doors to the closet and bathroom. Primary bathroom features a separate tub and shower and dual sinks with granite countertops. Down in the basement you'll find 995 unfinished square feet ready to be finished by you! The amenities at Edenwood are unmatched with multiple swimming pools, 2 water slides, a massive splash pad, tennis courts, and a playground! Don't wait! Make this beautiful home yours today.
